703826f-c.title: Brooklyn: Cortelyou Road - Troy Avenue
703826f-c.text:
(1)
4302 Cortelyou Road, south side, west from about Troy Ave., show-
ing the Cumming's homestead, at the S.E. corner of the Leffert's Cornwll
Right of Way.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same; another view, showing a portion af the Holy Cross
Cemetery.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(3)
The same, remedeled.
October 1928.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
